12. Bc4 b5 13. Nxf6+ Qxf6 14. Bxe6 Qxe6 15. Nc3 O-O 16. Nd5 Rac8 17. c3 {
Kokolias,K (2163)-Gantis,K (1955) Heraklion op 2011 (2) 1-0} Ne7 $11) 12. Nbc3
