19. Rfd1 Qf7 $15) 9... gxf6 10. N5c3 f5 {The typical Sveshnikov counterattack.}
11. Qh5 {Also typical for that opening.} (11. Bc4 Qg5 12. O-O Rg8 13. g3 f4 (
13... Be6) 14. Nd5 Rb8 15. Nbc3 {Fishbein, A (2490)-Polgar, J (2555) New York op
