$18) (10... Bb4 11. Nc3 O-O 12. Qc2 f5 13. exf6 Nxf6 14. Bg5 h6 15. Bh4 Bd6 16.
cxd5 exd5 $11 {Pranesh, M (2404)-Shyam, N (2465) Spilimbergo op 20th 2022 (9) 0-1
}) 11. Nd2 (11. b3 dxc4 12. Bxc4 Bxc4 13. bxc4 Bb4 14. Bd2 Nxe5 $1 $15 15. Rxe5
$2 Qd4 $19) 11... Bb4 $5 {Possibly an unnecessary refinement, inducing White
to weaken b3.} (11... Bc5 12. Qg4 Qb6 13. Re2 Bd4 {is also working.}) 12. a3 (
12. Qg4 O-O 13. a3 f5 14. exf6 Qxf6 15. Qxe6+ Qxe6 16. Rxe6 Bxd2 17. Bxd2 Nc5
18. Re3 Nxd3 19. Rxd3 Bxc4 $11) 12... Bc5 13. Qg4 Qb6 14. Re2 (14. Qg3 O-O)
14... Bd4 $13 15. Qxg7 (15. Qg3 Nc5 16. Bc2 O-O-O 17. Re1 dxc4 $13) 15... O-O-O
