33. Qe2 Qc1+ 34. Qe1 Qc6 $44) 32... e4 33. Bd4 (33. Nxe4 Bh4 {[%cal Gh6c6]
Threatening ...Qc6 with a double attack.} 34. Bf2 Bxf2 35. Kxf2 Qc6 36. Rb4 Bg6
37. Qc4+ Qxc4 38. Nf6+ Kf7 39. Rxc4 Kxf6 40. Rxf4+ Kxg7 $11 {With a probable
draw.}) 33... e3 34. Qg4 Bf6 35. Bxf6 Qxf6 36. Rf5 e2+ $5 (36... Qa6+ 37. Qe2
