e5 Bb5 20. Qd2 Rc6 $15 21. Nd4 $2 Nc4 $1 $19 {[%cal Gc6a6]}) (13. g4 b5 14. g5
b4 15. Ne2 e5 16. Qd3 Bb5 17. Qb3 Nd7 $17) 13... Bxf3 $1 $146 {It is a good
