delaying f2-f4, bearing the same idea of avoiding the lines with 9...e5.} Nxd4
{The usual continuation when White deviates from the normal lines.} 10. Qxd4 {
Hoping to gain a tempo with Qd2 if Black attacks the queen with ...e6-e5.} (10.
