Qb6 20. Qd2 Ne5 21. Rg3 f6 $11 {Kapusta,P (2157)-Manik,M (2374) Skalica op
2019 (3) 0-1}) 15. Qd2 Rfc8 $5 (15... Rac8 16. Rd1 Rfe8 17. Bd4 Nd7 $11 {
is more natural.}) 16. Rd1 Bd8 17. Rff1 Bb6 {An original way of exchanging the
