21... Bxd6 22. Qxd6 Be6 23. Rd1 Rd8 24. Qf4 Qb4 $44) 10... b6 (10... e5 11. Qd2
$14 {is what White was hoping for.}) (10... Bd7 11. f4 Bc6 12. Rad1 Qc7 {
