f3 {is slower.} Be7 12. g4 O-O 13. g5 ({Advancing the pawn all the way to h5
in order to prevent ...Nh5 is time consuming.} 13. h4 b4 14. Na4 Rb8 15. h5 Qe8
16. g5 Bxa4 17. gxf6 Bxf6 18. Kb1 Bb5 19. Nxb5 Qxb5 20. Qxb5 axb5 21. Rxd6 Nc4
22. Bxc4 bxc4 $11) 13... Nh5 {It would be sad if the knight had to retreat to
e8.} 14. f4 Nxb3+ 15. axb3 g6 $13) (11. Kb1 {is also a bit slow.} Be7 12. Bc1
O-O 13. Rhe1 b4 14. Na4 Nxb3 15. axb3 Qc7 16. g4 {Vocaturo,D (2603)-Van Wely,L
