Rxf5 (21. Rxd5 Rfe8 22. Qf3 g6 $17 {Martinez Lopez,D (2290)-Smirnov,A (2456)
La Roda op 42nd 2015 (7) 0-1}) 21... Rae8 $11) (15. Qd3 d5 16. c4 dxc4 17. Bxc4
Nd6 $11 18. Rac1 Nf5 (18... Nxc4 19. Rxc4 Bf6 $11) 19. Bf2 Qa5 20. g4 Nd6 21.
