solid. The knight over defends both f7 and b7, while also leaving the e-file
clear.} 23. Nf4 Bxe4 24. Bxe4 Rxe4 25. Ra7 Rb7 26. Nd5 Qb8 $13) 23. Nf4 Ne7 24.
Ra7 Rec8 (24... Nc8 $2 25. Nd5 Qd8 26. Raa1 Bxd5 27. exd5 $16 {Rieseler,C 
